Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kindaichi Case Files
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki, by the time you read this letter,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.24,0:01:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably, won't be in this world anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a really long relationship, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,From Kindergarten to Primary School, Secondary School \Nand High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always in the same class, with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.52,0:02:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In this way, before I die I'm trying
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to reminence about various scenes revolving,\Nlike a lantern.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.96,0:02:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Not, that I've actually seen one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.43,0:02:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Before dieing, I want to tell you...\Nmy feelings for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.30,0:02:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Facing you, and conveying my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Sorry! Hajime-chan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You waited...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The drama club's practice, just wouldn't\N finish until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever, who cares about something\N like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the blue face, Hajime-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.95,0:02:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still caught in, thinking about the \Nstomach examination?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My father, is going constantly too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm comming along too, so just relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, stop consoling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it for sure! I'm going \Nto die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, because this thing is just slightly painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have gone for the stomach examination,\N in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear wife, Kazue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:03:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When you've read this, I probably won't\N be in this world anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You and me, we've had a really long relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, before dieing I try to,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.52,0:03:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,remember various memories, that come\Nrevived as revolving lanterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... You guys, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I am here, for... a re-examination of\N the stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.77,0:03:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you too! I'm here for a rectal examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, there's still a change I might have polyp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Haha. So you're scared because of that, aren't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop saying nonsense! My body is\N hardcore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,As if, my body would give up so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Demon Inspector, of the First Investigation Division. \NThe disease scared him, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you showing off for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajime-chan, too! You were also scarred,\N up until a while ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.36,0:03:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say stupid things! I'm still young\N not old man, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, being this young suffering of disease!\N You don't get it, Kindaichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other side, the chances of dieing of Pokkuri, \Nwhilst young have
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,recently, become more often!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying!? You're not any different,\N old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! You too, also!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kindaichi-san! Please enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just gastritis, isn't it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The consultation won't hurt, will it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think so, then why don't you take\N  a look for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by myself!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This, is called a fiberscope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, take a look at the fibers, being so slender\N  as if made of glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It resembles a tied up bundle,\N  made of cord.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look here! Through this lens you can see, \N footage of the previous image.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is the inside of my stomach. \N This is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, after taking a look at It, It doesn't \N seem like such a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, It's gastritis! Just gastritis!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But, doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The inside of stomach is unexpectedly beautiful, \N  isn't it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The things I ate, looked delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You! Whatever you do, just don't become  \N a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Note: Onijima="Will-o'-the-Wisp Island"{\a6} \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.00,0:04:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,\N \N \N\N\N\N\NThe Onibijima Murder Case!{\a10} \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Part I{\a2} \N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, at the extra commotion you've caused, \NHajime-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.36,0:04:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hahaha. It's my bad, \Nmy bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, didn't Uncle Kenmochi\N come out yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:05:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows! A little latter then, Hajime-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,he entered the opposite medical examination room, \Nand just remained there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, It may be something serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again, I can give him a pat,\Non the shoulder!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because you're anxious, don't say\N  stupid things!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so. Hajime-chan, now I can travel with\N my mind at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, a trip? \N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget, or something!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,, Didn't we made plans to go somewhere, during \N our summer vacation!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that, If I'll die anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd keep eating fatty tuna, Salmon roe and sea urchin\N  at a Sushi Bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent all the money I earned, working part-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh? Wh... What's with that!? Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajime-chan. Because you said you were going,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I patiently endured not playing this summer,\N until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,, Instead, I could have worked part-time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... That's it! Hey, don't cut the\N talk short!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.52,0:05:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong! Take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,At what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparatory School for the Medical University.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Recruiting part-timers, for a Summer camp seminar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The location is south, to the small\N  island of Bousou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The Southern Country, is awkward to travel to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This sounds like It could be interesting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, we can earn pocket money too,\N killing two birds with one stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, looks like you put some though into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't over think It! It's totally decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... You'll drink something, right? All right,\N  today's my treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,, Ah. Jess, where do you keep going to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,, Ah. Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajime-chan, you can't enter someones hospital room without \N having permission in the fist place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He's, about the same age as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, this feels awesome, Hajime-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time on a fishing boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhuh ... this ship kind of little wiggly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhuh... The Gastritis, doesn't seem to be cured yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,, Hey, is your boyfriend doing alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shintani Yuri
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on is going to be pretty hard for two weeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hajime-chan! Shaken up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did we come all the way, when you can't \N even stand on your feet!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! You certainly said there's cook.\N  Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Shintani Yuri. But just Yuri is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, we'll be working colleagues\N  for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. By the way, since when is Yuri-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,, working in the Seminar House?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I just came in a week ago, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That Seminar House is called The Glory Hostel, but
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.82,0:08:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you can only attend when, students have vacation, in Summer, Winter and Autumn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, It's a growing seasonal training camp,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,they had to hire and recruit employees each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you can see it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That is The Glory Hostel, on the Shiranui island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The fishermen around here, seem to call it\N "The Will-o'-the-Wisp Island"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Will-o'-the-Wisp Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The Island, where those who cannot die came and\N the souls with a grudge gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, so said a legend once!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But, there are people who say, they really saw \N the will-o'-the-wisp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks for the good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the dorm leader, Tsukahara!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you! I'm Kindaichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm, Nanase Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be starting to work from today, \N immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,From tomorrow, the students will be arriving,\N one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:08:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But before that, I'll introduce you guy to the \Nother employees.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,First, there's a student same as you guys,\N working part-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm, Ohno Kouhei. I'm a 1.st year college student, but
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,because we're all colleagues, just treat me the you\N  would someone your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get along well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's our English teacher, Hanamura-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Her neighbor is, Kawasaki-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawasaki-san, aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe, from The Otemon Hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, It's me! You inspected the inside of my stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're the student from then, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because, Kindaichi is a rare name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But sensei, aren't you a doctor? Why are you working as a prep school teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawasaki-sensei, before becoming a doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,was a writer, who wrote many books, between which a math exams books,too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I too, also usually teacher at a high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Every instructor of this camp is a specialist employed for,\N  only short durations of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll also do good to come here, if you'll aim to ender the Medical University.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:10:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost all of the previous years students, passed the\N  tests to the school of choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look! This room here on the 2.nd floor, is the place the students attend lessons and reside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Room Nr. 6, the Hanazama Koubai's Ashibi room and the Ichou room,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Note: Ashibi= lily-of-the-valley;   Ichou= maidenhair tree {\a6}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shirakan room, the Baichijiku room and\N the Kinmokei room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Note: Shirakan= jap. white birch; Ichijiku= fig;  Kinmokei= fragrant olive  {\a6}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They've, all been made facing south.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In the western Hall of Books, there is no window \Nto the south of the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.02,0:10:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's western, the autumn-like room, and facing\N eastward the crape myrtle room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The place that we're staying on the 1.st floor, is of\Nthe same structure, isn't It?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this building basically is,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,made with an emphasis on day, more\N than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you guess, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, it was a old hotel once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Close!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, here was a sanatorium.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanatorium!?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Tuberculosis patients needing recuperation, have to go to the hospital for medical treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.98,0:10:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, the scary image of tuberculosis\N dissipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past, It was a dreadful disease, having to be hospitalized for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that so, Ohno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite knowledgeable, Nanase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there maybe a doctor or something in \Nyour house, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! In my house...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,, is just Bonbi! Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys get along pretty well. Are you\N perhaps lovers?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Hahaha That could not be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The outrageous of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just childhood friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that outrageous!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you saying? Don't tell me just so little!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that. Enough... Hahaha. Well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then It seems I'm going, \N to enjoy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, I get to work together with a girl and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,because she has a boyfriend, It's boring now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-- What's, with this affectionate bastard!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.69,0:11:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then for the time being you guys should \Nclean this room up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's " the blood of all hundred "?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Hajime-chan. That's read "crape myrtle" !
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, stop it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're....  Alright! Here's quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Between, the lily-of-the-valley room, the red-blossomed plum tree room\N and the maidenhair tree room,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Note: Ashibi room, Koubai room, Ichou room {\a6}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the white Japanese birch room, the fig room, the fragrant olive room
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirakanba room, Ichijiku room, Kinmokusei room{\a6}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's just a room left out, from all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then! Which one is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:12:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What, then! The Ashibi room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not enough color in the Kanji, so you \Ncan't read it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Note: Kanji= Chinese characters, used in Japan. {\a6}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There's just a figure partially colorless, isn't It?\NThere color, isn't it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, stop it you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hahaha. Well. then how about a quiz from me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This room remains vacant every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,After the Summer course It's to be opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only that, which was used only at 2.3 degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,, Can you get what's with that? Why is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You, can't you even understand something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "crape myrtle". Just experiment a little and\N you'll slip right through!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Because It's bad luck, right? Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Ohno-san! Why do we have to clean up the room,\Nif It's not in use?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, It's for the sake of it. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more to it, that room has quite an \Nrare and interesting history!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When you don't clean the room, It's said \Nbad things will happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, bad things? No way, what things will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when tomorrow the 15th of August comes,\NI'll tell you all about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That is if, you pass the cleaning test, \Nby not omitting anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:12:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The 15th of August? Is there something special,\N about this day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's just a trifling tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that it!? This room doesn't seem any different!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.19,0:13:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki, what are you doing? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This door. in between rooms seems to be connected\N to The Fragrant Olive Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't open! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's, of course impossible! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Take a good look! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. It's nailed shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,However, since how many months has it not been \Nclean here anymore for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself and clean properly!\N Ah! I'll quit, I'll quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This room isn't used anyways, is It?\N Cleaning it up is useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But, we'll get scolded, won't we? 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's way! It's just as Ohno-san said, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't clean up, bad things will happen! I'm, \Ntesting that out, to see what happens!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hajime-chan, you keep saying clever things, again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that!? Are you scared, Miyukii? \N It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go saying that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,These subs have been provided by (S.I.R ) {\a6}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kindaichi Case Files
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy & support subbing Kindaichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, finally the students have arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of the honorable students here are,\N the offspring of famous doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Be earnest, and try not to make any clumsy mistakes! \N Come on, smile, smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hahhahhahha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's okay! Just the sound was loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine! Just let me be!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's, the hell with you!? I wand to help...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen, Shiina-kun!? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. He just fell! You're, just useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you didn't dropped my bag, did you now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me, Kato-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You there, do you have a problem or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, me... !? Not really!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're somehow less than I expected, hearing \Nyou were collage students!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.83,0:14:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop messing around! You're just a part-time \Nemployee, aren't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!? I'm a employee!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.03,0:14:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're just a worker, then mind your\N own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:15:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't concern yourself with us, if you know,\N what's good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Morimura, wanna get this guy!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.25,0:15:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with these guys!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If Hajime-chan did something bad,\N I will apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that a little while ago must've \Nbeen troublesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come to a meddlesome place,\N to work at!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have thought that, right? But, \Nyou can't run away anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Until, at least the ship carrying the students,\N comes in three day. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless, there's extreme circumstances, you \Ncan't leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Even ourselves, the students, are prohibited,\N from using the telephone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's, almost like a spartan training camp,\N isn't it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way!? Who are you? 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my bad, my bad! I'm Kawashima Jukata, a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You can call either Yukata or Yuta, \Nas you well please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's reassuring to know that, there's people here,\N such as Kawashima too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:16:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that!? They're all very unusual, \Naren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,, I meant, the students of this seminar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, seem like it! Particularly, to trio you entwined in 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,First, there's Pashiri, who lost to Shiina and \Nthat Kato is the number two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And the one with the most arrogant\N looking eyes is,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.81,0:16:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,, Morimura Keiichi, or so he's called!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, he's a guy who pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Above all, Morimura is the son of the surgeon Otemon, who's the head of the hospital board.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This hostel, is owned by Otemon and \Nthe seminar too. 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The management of our high school is also \Ndirected by Mr. Otemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's annoying, Kawashima-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ota!? Once Morimura hears about this, you 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,will be kicked off from school!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just a joke, Aya-chan! I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so over-familiar and stop  \Ncalling me, Aya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your familiar tone is what pisses me off,\N the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Say... You won't actually rat me out to Morimura,\N wiil you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you did that, then I would also talk about,\Nwhat I saw Ebisawa ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.58,0:16:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebisawa!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm not mistaken ... Didn't I heard that name,\N somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! That's it for the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.66,0:17:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you to get along well, \Nwith each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, we'll be living together for\N two weeks. So you guys, get long!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you! Ohno-san ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Can you come over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you to, Kindaichi-kun \Nand Nanase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a collage student, Shiraishi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.18,0:17:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is perfect timing! Actually, now
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,can go you go around and contact everyone,\N telling them to gather here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, is August the 15th.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The glory hostel will begin commencing the annual,\N Midnight Test of Courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The test of courage? You can't mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the traditional event, that you Ohno-san,\Ntalked about earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It's being held here every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, the study for the difficult exams,\N will begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And before that, well, you can make some\N good memories, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What... !? What kind of test of courage will it be? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it! You guys still don't know about it,\N do you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, in this glory hostel, there's \Na trifling ghost story!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghost story? That's right,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,they're actually appear, that is the ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The story about this place is famous among,\Nthe locals here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, says it this way, by calling   \N"Demons of the midnight"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then! Kindaichi-kun and Nanase-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,are to be initiated to this glory hostel, by listening \Nto the terrible legend! 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Morimura-kun and Shiina-kun still aren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawashima-kun, also didn't come yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,, Morimura and Shiina aren't participatig, also.\N They studying, tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Kawashima-kun will also be joining us. But \N  he'll appear in a different form.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Another Former? Well, this glory hostel was
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,originally a sanatorium. You all know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, while that may be true, making this\N into a prep school dorm,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is still allowed. There's nothing saying,\N anything against that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But, only as long no one is allowed use that room, I think! \NThe Scape Myrtle room, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:19:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because, that room is a path,\N for evil spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumors began to start ghost willl appear between the crape myrtle
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It was about 10 years ago, when
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that year, a student who failed to pass the exams, of his school of choice, lost his life by his own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.95,0:19:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Those, who took part in the seminar that time, \N have remained waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In the crape myrtle room!? Eh'm ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,During the summer of that year, on August the 15th a ghost appeared for tghe first time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain student saw it at midnight, while \Nwaking up to use the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment, he passed in front of,\N the crape myrtle room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,From the room that nobody should be in, \Nhe heard a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The student, who became curios, took a peek in, \Nthrough the keyhole.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The student rushed to get the key, unlocking the door, \Nto take another look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But, there was nothing and no one inside it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.49,0:19:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, he though that his eyes played,\N a trick on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.50,0:19:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That student, who saw The Will-o'-The-Wisp,\N through keyhole,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The next morning, near the Crape Myrtle room,\N just below in a pond,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a floating corpse, in a body bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! I don't want to hear anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! That's the hole story!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, It's about time we begin soon,\N right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Glory Hostels Midnight legendary,\N test of corage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh!? Starting from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a newbie and a man, right? Of course, \Nyou're the first choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's, a rule from long ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, I don't want to. That's like\N poison tasting, isn't it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're, pitiful! And you still call yourself, a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even, if you say It like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, If you don't hurry, you'll get past\N the 0:00 am!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh!? If I go it's alright, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.16,0:21:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh... !? What!? I can't see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that enough? Not yet, a bit longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.46,0:21:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's, still some 10 seconds to go,\N before 0:00 am!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,6・5・4
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,3・2・1・0
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.78,0:21:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? Do you see anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! He's... He's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Morimura!? Wh... !? - What is it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Some... ! - Is the something, inside? 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.81,0:21:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's, with the racket in the middle of the night,\N like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukahara-san, give me the key!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.96,0:22:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This... this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.46,0:23:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.40,0:23:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The corpse and criminal also, suddenly disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.03,0:23:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The next morning, Morimura-sans presence is nowhere to be seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.94,0:23:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The deed of evil spirits and the terrified Shiima-san, \Nunintentionally blurting out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.41,0:24:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebisawa...  You should do something about,\N the seminars practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.24,0:24:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, in midsummer white snow began to fall,\N on the island of The Will-o'-The-Wisp!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.85,0:24:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And the mystery of the footprints, that were left on the snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.68,0:24:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What, I saw previously!
